### BookStore API — esempi di chiamate
### Compatibile con VS Code REST Client e JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@apiKey = dev-key-1234

# ============================================================
# AUTENTICAZIONE
# ============================================================

### Richiesta senza API key → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres

### Richiesta con API key non valida → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres
X-API-Key: chiave-sbagliata

# ============================================================
# GENRES (sola lettura, pre-seeded)
# ============================================================

### Lista tutti i generi
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Dettaglio genere id=1 (Fiction)
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Tentativo di scrittura → 405
POST {{baseUrl}}/genres
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Nuovo Genere" }

# ============================================================
# PUBLISHERS
# ============================================================

### Crea un editore
# @name createPublisher
POST {{baseUrl}}/publishers
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mondadori"
}

### Lista editori (paginata)
GET {{baseUrl}}/publishers
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Lista editori con ricerca
GET {{baseUrl}}/publishers?search=mondo
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Lista editori pagina 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/publishers?page=2&limit=5
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Dettaglio editore (con book_count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/publishers/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Aggiorna nome editore
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/publishers/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mondadori Libri"
}

### Elimina editore (senza libri → 204, con libri → 409)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/publishers/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Errore: name mancante → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/publishers
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Errore: nome duplicato → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/publishers
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mondadori"
}

# ============================================================
# AUTHORS
# ============================================================

### Crea un autore (campi minimi)
POST {{baseUrl}}/authors
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Umberto",
  "last_name": "Eco"
}

### Crea un autore (tutti i campi)
POST {{baseUrl}}/authors
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Isaac",
  "last_name": "Asimov",
  "birth_date": "1920-01-02",
  "biography": "Autore americano di fantascienza e divulgazione scientifica.",
  "nationality": "American"
}

### Lista autori
GET {{baseUrl}}/authors
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Lista autori con ricerca per nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/authors?search=eco
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Dettaglio autore (con lista libri)
GET {{baseUrl}}/authors/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Aggiornamento parziale autore
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/authors/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nationality": "Italian",
  "biography": "Semiologo, filosofo e romanziere italiano."
}

### Elimina autore (senza libri → 204)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/authors/2
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Errore: first_name mancante → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/authors
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "last_name": "Eco"
}

### Errore: autore con libri → 409
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/authors/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

# ============================================================
# BOOKS
# ============================================================

### Crea un libro (modello base)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Il Nome della Rosa",
  "isbn": "9780156001311",
  "author": "Umberto Eco",
  "price": 12.99,
  "category": "Fiction"
}

### Crea un altro libro
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Foundation",
  "isbn": "9780553293357",
  "author": "Isaac Asimov",
  "price": 9.99,
  "category": "Sci-Fi"
}

### Lista libri (default: page=1, limit=20, sort=title asc)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Lista libri ordinati per prezzo crescente
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?sort=price&order=asc
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Lista libri con filtro titolo (case-insensitive, parziale)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?title=rosa
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Lista libri disponibili (quantity > 0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?available=true
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Lista libri con paginazione esplicita
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?page=1&limit=5
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Dettaglio libro (eager loading: publisher, authors, genres)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Aggiornamento parziale libro
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/books/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 14.50,
  "title": "Il Nome della Rosa (Edizione speciale)"
}

### Elimina libro → 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Errore: ISBN duplicato → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Altro libro stesso ISBN",
  "isbn": "9780156001311",
  "author": "Chiunque",
  "price": 5.00,
  "category": "Fiction"
}

### Errore: ISBN non valido → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Libro test",
  "isbn": "ISBN-NON-VALIDO",
  "author": "Autore",
  "price": 9.99,
  "category": "Fiction"
}

### Errore: prezzo negativo → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Libro test",
  "isbn": "9780553293364",
  "author": "Autore",
  "price": -1,
  "category": "Fiction"
}

### Errore: id non numerico → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/abc
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Errore: libro non trovato → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/99999
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Errore: sort non valido → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?sort=colonna_inesistente
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Errore: limit > 100 → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?limit=500
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
